1.7
log
@Don't try to use grantpt() on OpenBSD. It causes crashes.

Problem reported by Jan Stary and Marcus Merighi, analysed by guenther@@,
configure.ac patch by me.
@
text
@dnl  Copyright 2005 Red Hat, Inc.
